          "Frusemide 1 mg/kg IV/PO if heart failure features",
          "Oxygen to maintain SpO2 ≥75% (cyanotic lesions) or ≥94% (acyanotic)",
          "Correct metabolic acidosis with bicarbonate if pH <7.2",
